casebody.data:
No. 125,

Misc.

Biloche v. United States. Petitioner pro se. Solicitor General Cox, Assistant Attorney General Miller and Beatrice Rosenberg for the United States.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit denied without prejudice to future certiorari proceedings to review the further actions of the courts below on petitioner’s application to appeal his conviction in forma pauperis as suggested by the Solicitor General.
